# Design System: UI Components & Tokens

Dieses Projekt verwendet ShadCN UI mit strikten Design Tokens. Native HTML-Elemente sind verboten.

---

## 1. Komponenten-Governance

### Verbotene Native Elemente

| ❌ Verboten | ✅ Verwende stattdessen | Import |
|-------------|-------------------------|--------|
| `<button>` | `<Button>` | `@/components/ui/button` |
| `<input>` | `<Input>` | `@/components/ui/input` |
| `<textarea>` | `<Textarea>` | `@/components/ui/textarea` |
| `<select>` | `<Select>` | `@/components/ui/select` |
| `<table>` | `<Table>` | `@/components/ui/table` |
| `<dialog>` | `<Dialog>` | `@/components/ui/dialog` |
| `<label>` | `<Label>` | `@/components/ui/label` |
| `<input type="checkbox">` | `<Checkbox>` | `@/components/ui/checkbox` |
| `<input type="radio">` | `<RadioGroup>` | `@/components/ui/radio-group` |
| `<a href="/intern">` | `<Link href="/intern">` | `next/link` |

### Erlaubte Ausnahmen
```tsx
// ✅ Externe Links
<a href="https://example.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">

// ✅ mailto/tel
<a href="mailto:kontakt@example.com">

// ✅ Hidden/File Inputs
<input type="hidden" name="csrf" value={token} />
<input type="file" onChange={handleUpload} />

// ✅ Innerhalb von src/components/ui/ (ShadCN wraps native elements)
```

