## 2. Design Tokens

### Farben (Semantisch)

| Element-Typ | Hintergrund | Text | Border |
|:------------|:------------|:-----|:-------|
| **Seite/Body** | `bg-background` | `text-foreground` | - |
| **Card/Container** | `bg-card` | `text-card-foreground` | `border-border` |
| **Dialog/Modal** | `bg-popover` | `text-popover-foreground` | `border-border` |
| **Primär-Aktion** | `bg-primary` | `text-primary-foreground` | - |
| **Sekundär-Aktion** | `bg-secondary` | `text-secondary-foreground` | - |
| **Destruktiv** | `bg-destructive` | `text-destructive-foreground` | - |
| **Erfolg** | `bg-success` | `text-success` | - |
| **Warnung** | `bg-warning` | `text-warning` | - |
| **Info** | `bg-info` | `text-info` | - |
| **Metadaten/Tags** | `bg-muted` | `text-muted-foreground` | - |
| **Interaktiv (Hover)** | `bg-accent` | `text-accent-foreground` | - |
| **Inputs** | `bg-transparent` | `text-foreground` | `border-input` |

**VERBOTEN:** `bg-blue-500`, `text-red-600`, `text-[#333]`, `bg-[#ff0000]`

### Hover-States
```tsx
// Interaktive Listen
<div className="hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground">

// Buttons
<Button className="hover:bg-primary/90">
```

### Radius

| Klasse | Verwendung |
|:-------|:-----------|
| `rounded-sm` | Badges, Checkboxen |
| `rounded-md` | Buttons, Inputs (Standard) |
| `rounded-lg` | Cards, Modals |
| `rounded-xl` | Große Container |
| `rounded-full` | Avatare, Pills |

**VERBOTEN:** `rounded-[8px]`, `rounded-2xl`, `rounded-3xl`

### Spacing (Strikte Skala)

**Erlaubte Werte:** `0`, `1`, `2`, `4`, `6`, `8`, `12`, `16`, `24`, `32`, `48`, `64`

| Kontext | Empfehlung |
|:--------|:-----------|
| Kleine Abstände | `gap-1`, `gap-2` |
| Button Padding | `px-6 py-2`, `p-4` |
| Card Padding | `p-6`, `p-8` |
| Sektions-Abstände | `py-12`, `py-16` |

**VERBOTEN:** `p-3`, `m-5`, `gap-7`, `p-[17px]`, `m-[23px]`

### Typografie

| Element | Klassen |
|:--------|:--------|
| H1 | `text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight` oder `text-4xl` |
| H2 | `text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight` |
| H3 | `text-xl font-semibold` |
| H4 | `text-lg font-medium` |
| Body | `text-base leading-relaxed` |
| Small | `text-sm text-muted-foreground` |
| Tiny | `text-xs text-muted-foreground` |

**VERBOTEN:** `text-[13px]`, `text-[18px]`, `leading-[1.7]`

